--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

System Architecture

arch ---> gives the system architecture  Eg: x86_64 or 32 bit



32 bit and 64 bit

- main difference is the number of calculations they can do at a time, you can run 32 bit applications
  on a 64 bit system but not vice versa. 


